00:51:51.167 --> 00:51:53.876
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:51:59.626 --> 00:52:14.918
As I told you yesterday, that truth is what it is and we have to keep our mind open as scientists to see what is the truth.

00:52:26.876 --> 00:52:39.042
We cannot organize the truth, and we cannot change the truth, and we cannot ourselves create the truth.

00:52:47.834 --> 00:52:51.375
So what we can do is to know the truth,

00:52:55.709 --> 00:52:57.042
to become the truth,

00:53:00.083 --> 00:53:01.792
and to enjoy the truth.

00:53:05.626 --> 00:53:08.751
It's very abstract if I talk of truth.

00:53:12.751 --> 00:53:20.792
But how do we know truth normally? Is through our sense organs.

00:53:28.209 --> 00:53:35.792
Like, you see all these flowers, and you see through your eyes these are flowers, and you know it is the flowers.

00:53:45.042 --> 00:53:55.334
Anything that you hear, all of you hear the same thing, and you know that's what is the truth what you are hearing.

00:54:02.125 --> 00:54:08.209
Now, you can feel something hot or cold with your fingertips.

00:54:13.834 --> 00:54:19.584
And whatever you can feel with your fingertips is the truth that you know.

00:54:26.417 --> 00:54:38.417
But in darkness, if you are holding the snake in your hand and somebody says, "You are holding the snake," you can always say that "No, I believe it's a rope, it's not the snake."

00:54:50.667 --> 00:54:53.083
So, to know that, you have to have the light.

00:54:58.000 --> 00:55:03.834
In human evolution, we have known many more things than the animals quality.

00:55:10.751 --> 00:55:20.000
For example, if you take a dog or a horse through a dirty lane, he won't feel the filth, he won't have any bad smells, he'll just pass through.

00:55:31.209 --> 00:55:32.626
But we cannot.

00:55:35.584 --> 00:55:41.542
In the same way, we can understand aesthetics, which a dog cannot understand.

00:55:49.250 --> 00:56:04.334
We can understand who are the painters and who are better painters — everything we understand with our understanding of the art and music, which is only a human﻿00:00:00:00 00:00:05:00 (Yogi talks in German)

00:56:19.083 --> 00:56:23.000
But actually in this area a confusion starts.

00:56:26.501 --> 00:56:33.167
Some people might say that it's a good… good music, some will say it's not good, somebody will say it's bad.

00:56:42.042 --> 00:56:47.667
At this stage, the ego starts deciding: "I like this. I like that. I like that."

00:56:54.834 --> 00:56:59.876
So this ego creates a problem between us and the truth.

00:57:06.042 --> 00:57:11.626
As shown in this picture, the ego is the yellow part on our head.

00:57:16.626 --> 00:57:19.709
We have given it the colour of the bile.

00:57:21.334 --> 00:57:22.417
YOGINI: Excuse me, Mother?

00:57:22.876 --> 00:57:24.667
SHRI MATAJI: Bile. Of the bile.

00:57:30.375 --> 00:57:35.876
When you have too much bile, then ego starts bubbling more.

00:57:40.250 --> 00:57:46.709
That means with the overactivity of the liver you get your ego overdeveloped.

00:57:54.999 --> 00:58:05.042
Yesterday I told you about the cancer disease, but today I'll tell you how much this horrible liver can cost us trouble.

00:58:14.042 --> 00:58:29.459
Actually, when you think too much, then your grey cells are to be transformed — or could be replaced — only by this Swadhishthana Chakra, which is on… working more on the Sun line.

00:58:41.125 --> 00:58:52.792
And the Swadhishthana is put to too much strain, and it neglects your liver, it neglects your pancreas, neglects your spleen and your kidneys.

00:59:05.501 --> 00:59:13.083
As a result of that, too much heat is liberated because liver cannot work any more

00:59:19.125 --> 00:59:20.751
as it becomes so worried.

00:59:23.709 --> 00:59:33.417
With this heat, you get the phlegm melting away, and that's how you will get all these problems of cold, hay fever, sneezing, asthma.

00:59:40.542 --> 00:59:47.125
Then, at the pancreas, as the pancreas also becomes overactive, you develop diabetes.

00:59:52.459 --> 01:00:02.417
In Indian villages, a villager would not take tea unless and until the spoon stands at right angles in the sugar.

01:00:09.751 --> 01:00:11.375
But they never get diabetes.

01:00:13.834 --> 01:00:23.999
Only those people who are futuristic and think too much all the time get diabetes, and then from kidney they get high blood pressure and tensions.

01:00:36.918 --> 01:00:47.834
So, on one side, we are covered by the ego, and on the other side, by our conditioning, which is a superego; and that's how we are cut out from the truth.

01:00:58.999 --> 01:01:06.209
So, to know the truth, what we have to do is to remove both these things, which are covering our brain.

01:01:13.918 --> 01:01:32.999
And as I told you yesterday, that when Kundalini rises, She pierces through this centre of Christ, and the whole of your conditioning and ego is sucked in; and that's how this portion opens up and you get your Self-realization, and you might feel the cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:01:55.375 --> 01:02:05.501
At this time, you find from your fingertips, as you've found yesterday, a kind of a cool breeze blowing inside.

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:16.334
Also you have found yesterday a cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:02:25.542 --> 01:02:30.000
Many people doubt first, that it might be some window is open or something.

01:02:35.959 --> 01:02:38.417
Yes, of course the window is open — but in your head.

01:02:42.709 --> 01:02:46.167
And that's how you have felt the cool breeze coming out of it.

01:02:50.542 --> 01:02:56.626
This happening is described very well in the ancient scriptures, in all the scriptures.

01:03:01.375 --> 01:03:07.918
In some scriptures, it is described in a little ambiguous manner, or a mysterious manner.

01:03:12.999 --> 01:03:24.209
But very clearly it is described by certain saints of India who have very secretly given Self-realization to very few people in the past.

01:03:33.751 --> 01:03:38.918
As I told you, this is a living process of a living energy of evolution.

01:03:46.167 --> 01:03:56.083
But beyond these two channels that you've seen, we have some other problems, which are very serious, and we are not aware of them.

01:04:04.834 --> 01:04:11.042
One of them are on the left-hand side, as you know; is the collective subconscious area.

01:04:18.876 --> 01:04:25.292
This area has… has in it all that is dead, since our creation.

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:38.709
And on the right-hand side, you have, at the extreme, something called the collective supraconscious.

01:04:44.584 --> 01:04:53.626
That is what… all the dead who have been very futuristic.

01:04:54.792 --> 01:04:58.125
Contains all the dead who have been very futuristic people.

01:05:06.542 --> 01:05:15.751
So now, when there is evil, when you see evil… so many will say there is no evil — because they must be evil themselves — but there is evil.

01:05:24.501 --> 01:05:33.375
This evil crawls into us from the left or from the right, from the collective subconscious or the collective supraconscious.

01:05:40.999 --> 01:05:58.042
When you see many people who go to false gurus and lose all their money, everything, and become bankrupt, and then become recluses, you are surprised that how educated people get into such troubles.

01:06:11.584 --> 01:06:18.626
Even if you, say, do any religion as such, they also end up into this area very fast.

01:06:24.626 --> 01:06:35.584
I'll tell you, in India now we have Hinduism, which is actually basically based on the ascent of human beings, like… or any other religion.

01:06:47.959 --> 01:07:01.417
But if you go to these temples and… during the time when the Goddess is worshipped for nine days, you'll be amazed that we have all kinds of possessed people, dancing and doing all kinds of funny gestures.

01:07:16.626 --> 01:07:29.167
Now, these are all possessed people and — possessed women, and they are mostly maidservants — and they can tell you the name of the horse which is going to win in the races.

01:07:37.918 --> 01:07:43.292
They can tell you all kinds of nonsensical thing which has nothing to do with God or with the Goddess.

01:07:49.792 --> 01:07:59.999
So now we have, say, another religion, which we call as Jainism, who believe in vegetarianism to such an extent that they cannot even kill mosquitoes.

01:08:12.209 --> 01:08:25.125
They get a man inside a hut and put all the little little bugs inside, so the bugs should suck the blood of that man; and they'll revere that man because he has given blood to so many bugs.

01:08:35.334 --> 01:08:49.751
Then we have some Buddhists, who go on having some sort of a… (moves Her hand as if rotating a rattle) what you call… a kind of a… round moving chakras (wheels); goes on humming, humming, humming like mad.

01:08:56.501 --> 01:08:59.459
By doing that, are you going to get your ascent?

01:09:05.125 --> 01:09:09.959
By moving those wheels, are we going to rise in our evolution?

01:09:16.042 --> 01:09:26.626
And they think that by beating on the… vertebral column, beating on this column, vertebral column, that they can raise the Kundalini.

01:09:32.209 --> 01:09:34.459
And they can go to any extreme, the beat.

01:09:38.292 --> 01:09:41.792
Basically, behind all these things is money-making.

01:09:46.250 --> 01:09:51.501
All these lamas and all these are making lots of money, and they have too much gold with them.

01:09:57.501 --> 01:09:58.792
Now you come to Islam.

01:10:00.501 --> 01:10:07.999
And you find that in Islamic religion same thing: people are just quarrelling and fighting; now you see Iraq, Iran — it's mad thing.

01:10:15.999 --> 01:10:17.542
Then you come to Christianity.

01:10:20.042 --> 01:10:22.417
Christianity is the religion of compassion.

01:10:26.959 --> 01:10:29.792
But Christians are the cruellest people you could think.

01:10:34.334 --> 01:10:39.834
When they went to America, they killed all the aboriginals.

01:10:39.834 --> 01:10:47.167
In South America, you can't find one person who can be called as a Red Indian, not one person.

01:10:55.459 --> 01:11:01.542
They came to India with a… one… gun in one hand and Bible in another hand.

01:11:08.042 --> 01:11:16.250
Are they the disciples of Christ, who said: "O My Father, please forgive them because they do not know what they are doing"?

01:11:25.501 --> 01:11:29.999
Christ has said: "Thou shalt not have any adulterous eyes."

01:11:35.209 --> 01:11:40.626
Have you found any… even Christian priests who are… who haven't got adulterous eyes?

01:11:48.000 --> 01:11:54.792
So, when we see religion becoming so funny and perverted, we start losing faith in God.

01:12:03.542 --> 01:12:05.667
And many people believe there is no God.

01:12:08.209 --> 01:12:10.501
But I think this is very unscientific.

01:12:14.167 --> 01:12:24.334
You must find out the truth, is there God or not, is there a Creator or not.

01:12:25.042 --> 01:12:35.250
Without finding it out, if you just say there is no God, because you've seen all this religious nonsense, you must know that you have done no justice to your creator.

01:12:44.999 --> 01:12:56.999
All these great Incarnations, and all these prophets, and all these great people who came on this Earth to establish proper religion — have been misused!

01:13:05.167 --> 01:13:07.667
Have been… they have been used for money-making!

01:13:11.125 --> 01:13:12.542
Or for power!

01:13:15.667 --> 01:13:17.459
They have nothing to do with God.

01:13:20.250 --> 01:13:27.209
But God exists — and now can be proved when you get your Self-realization.

01:13:32.125 --> 01:13:39.042
Actually, Buddha felt: no use talking about God; because if you talk about God, they'll forget about Self-realization.

01:13:39.042 --> 01:13:43.667
So He said, "First I'll tell them about Self-realization, Self-realization, Self-realization."

01:13:56.375 --> 01:14:05.501
So now I have to tell you that this Power resides within you, which is coiled up in three and a half coils within yourself.

01:14:12.709 --> 01:14:18.542
And this Power has to manifest itself in these modern times in a big way.

01:14:25.250 --> 01:14:29.334
Of course, you cannot pay for it, it is too invaluable.

01:14:33.542 --> 01:14:34.751
And it works out.

01:14:35.417 --> 01:14:43.709
Not only works out but it helps you to get rid of most of your problems, and you become a very powerful personality.

01:14:53.501 --> 01:14:59.000
Your compassion doesn't become just a talk, talk, but it becomes effective.

01:15:04.751 --> 01:15:05.584
It works.

01:15:07.751 --> 01:15:20.876
Because this all-pervading Power, which starts flowing through you, is a thinking power, understanding power, is intelligence.

01:15:32.167 --> 01:15:37.584
It organizes, it cooperates. Above all, it loves.

01:15:43.834 --> 01:15:45.918
It's such a great thing to discover it!

01:15:49.375 --> 01:15:51.918
And also to discover about yourself.

01:15:55.584 --> 01:15:59.334
Which is such a glorious, beautiful thing!

01:16:04.542 --> 01:16:09.626
And it has to work out in a big way.

01:16:11.709 --> 01:16:20.292
It has been already predicted all over in so many ways that this was the time for it to work out.

01:16:26.876 --> 01:16:29.125
There have been never so many seekers!

01:16:32.999 --> 01:16:38.999
It's the special category, which William Blake has described as "men of God".

01:16:46.626 --> 01:16:57.918
And he has said… he has said that these men of God will know themselves and they will have power to make others know themselves.

01:17:07.417 --> 01:17:12.417
So it's very important to understand the value of human life.

01:17:18.167 --> 01:17:21.167
That you are at the epitome of your evolution.

01:17:25.999 --> 01:17:33.834
And with this last happening, you will break through into that new realm of a realized personality.

01:17:42.334 --> 01:17:46.667
Whatever I may say, you have not to take Me for granted.

01:17:52.918 --> 01:18:05.834
You yourself have to experience it, and see for yourself, and achieve your complete establishment into the truth.

01:18:12.167 --> 01:18:13.999
Truth which is Divine Love.

01:18:17.999 --> 01:18:19.167
So may God bless you!

01:18:27.626 --> 01:18:32.250
If you have any questions, I would like to answer them.

01:18:32.918 --> 01:18:37.375
