01:21:27.167 --> 01:21:31.459
You don't have to decide. Your Kundalini knows.

01:21:33.250 --> 01:21:34.667
Everybody is worthy of it.

01:21:43.375 --> 01:21:45.083
You don't have to judge yourself.

01:21:47.792 --> 01:21:49.417
Only keep happy, that's all.

01:21:54.626 --> 01:21:57.626
(A seeker asks a question in German)

01:21:59.292 --> 01:22:00.292
YOGINI: What is the purpose of—

01:22:00.292 --> 01:22:02.334
YOGI: What is the meaning of Self-realization?

01:22:02.459 --> 01:22:03.501
SHRI MATAJI: Oh, Self…

01:22:04.834 --> 01:22:19.000
The purpose of Self-realization is to know your Self, where the Self is the embodiment of truth and embodiment of joy.

01:22:20.542 --> 01:22:36.751
And when you have Self-realization, then your attention becomes active and knows everything; apart from that, it works out all the problems.

01:22:39.542 --> 01:22:40.709
(Laughing) It's a big question.

01:23:04.375 --> 01:23:08.626
First of all, all your physical problems are solved. Most of them.

01:23:14.083 --> 01:23:19.792
Then your mental, emotional, spiritual problems are solved.

01:23:26.042 --> 01:23:30.626
You do not get into any tensions, you become a very kind personality.

01:23:31.876 --> 01:23:32.959
(Repeating to yogini) Any tensions.

01:23:39.584 --> 01:23:43.999
Then you start seeing everything as a drama.

01:23:49.918 --> 01:23:53.999
Now, if you are in the water, you are afraid of getting drowned.

01:23:54.334 --> 01:23:59.584
But supposing you are in the boat — then you see it, you don't mind… anything.

01:24:08.501 --> 01:24:15.584
But if you are a master swimmer, then you are not afraid of anything, and you can make others also master swimmers.

01:24:23.417 --> 01:24:26.334
Then you become collectively conscious.

01:24:26.334 --> 01:24:34.999
Is becoming; again I say, you become, it's not just mental, that "we are all brothers and sisters", or in just like just you will start reading each other's thoughts.

01:24:43.959 --> 01:24:48.876
You start feeling another personality within yourself on your fingertips.

01:24:54.375 --> 01:24:58.292
So you realize that innate relationship between you and others.

01:25:05.918 --> 01:25:19.792
Then you get over all kinds of racialism, all kinds of false ideas of religion, or conditioning, of a country, this, that — all the nonsense that's going on.

01:25:29.918 --> 01:25:32.834
Now, supposing you become a democratic country.

01:25:36.334 --> 01:25:39.375
Then, at the extreme, you become very money-oriented.

01:25:45.626 --> 01:25:47.083
Terrible competitions,

01:25:49.209 --> 01:25:52.959
when the individual is given [utter] importance and collective [has none].

01:26:00.876 --> 01:26:02.999
So such a country again goes down.

01:26:07.876 --> 01:26:11.209
But supposing you are a communist.

01:26:14.083 --> 01:26:20.792
Then you… you become very strong in your collective, but individually you go down.

01:26:26.209 --> 01:26:29.459
Because you have no value for the individual.

01:26:33.167 --> 01:26:36.292
As a result, your individual suffers.

01:26:40.918 --> 01:26:50.709
But when you get your Self-realization, then every individual is nourished, and the collective becomes strong.

01:26:59.667 --> 01:27:06.375
Now, we have about fifty or sixty nations from where we have Sahaja Yogis.

01:27:11.876 --> 01:27:14.626
Numberless. Quite a lot.

01:27:15.250 --> 01:27:20.334
Germany, of course, is not so good, I must say. Not so many. I don't know why.

01:27:27.999 --> 01:27:34.209
But I have never seen anybody quarrelling, fighting, saying bad words, hurting…

01:27:43.709 --> 01:27:53.918
If sometimes somebody does hurt someone, again he is… apologises and tries to be all right — because he sees what's wrong with him.

01:28:02.709 --> 01:28:05.876
And he doesn't like it. He just throws away.

01:28:10.083 --> 01:28:14.334
Unless and until we can see ourselves, how are we going to correct?

01:28:22.999 --> 01:28:30.083
But it's not mental, it just works out through the awakening and reawakening of Kundalini.

01:28:35.834 --> 01:28:38.209
And the complete transformation takes place.

01:28:42.834 --> 01:28:48.083
There is no question of any war or any kind of a conflict.

01:28:54.667 --> 01:28:58.250
Everybody is in complete joy and happiness.

01:29:03.375 --> 01:29:09.792
The marriages are successful, the children are beautiful — and it's a new world, and a new age.

01:29:19.083 --> 01:29:23.042
This transformation is needed for the emancipation of humanity.

01:29:28.999 --> 01:29:34.042
We have all these institutions like United Nations, this, that.

01:29:34.250 --> 01:29:38.667
What work are they doing? They have not given any transformation.

01:29:47.792 --> 01:29:54.667
This is what it is. This is the purpose in the transformation of human beings into their beauty and glory.

01:30:14.459 --> 01:30:17.459
It's quite a small question — and a big answer.

01:30:21.125 --> 01:30:31.000
