(Yogi translates the question to Shri Mataji)

01:37:51.709 --> 01:37:54.209
Maybe. Also karmas.

01:37:54.459 --> 01:37:58.000
But in realization your karmas are all sucked in.

01:38:14.083 --> 01:38:18.709
