(Yogi translates the question to Shri Mataji)

01:38:25.334 --> 01:38:28.542
Yes, practically most of them. Practically most of them.

01:38:28.542 --> 01:38:33.167
But if something is dead and all that, then you could say we cannot do it.

01:38:33.167 --> 01:38:39.542
For example, if there's a cataract, we will not be able to cure a cataract.

01:38:40.626 --> 01:38:48.083
Or something dead. You see, supposing there's a fibroid, or some sort of things there are. So many people cannot be cured.

01:39:00.918 --> 01:39:03.000
You see, unless and until you get your…

01:39:03.751 --> 01:39:06.167
(To yogini) Huh? She's asking question?

01:39:06.167 --> 01:39:07.834
YOGINI: No.
SHRI MATAJI: (To a seeker) [UNCLEAR], madam?

01:39:08.417 --> 01:39:10.999
SEEKER: I just said [UNCLEAR] [I was fine].

