But there's one thing I must really, at the very outset, confess to you.

01:39:33.000 --> 01:39:39.542
At the very outset, I must confess to you something — that the Divine is common sense.

01:39:47.626 --> 01:39:48.834
It's not a doctor.

01:39:53.584 --> 01:39:59.959
It is only interested in people who will do divine work.

01:40:06.083 --> 01:40:10.334
