01:42:20.167 --> 01:42:23.250
So best thing is that you better have your Self-realization.

01:42:33.417 --> 01:42:40.167
At the very outset, I [would again] request you to do few things which are very simple.

01:42:47.584 --> 01:42:50.626
One of them is that you have to take out your shoes.

01:42:55.375 --> 01:42:59.209
This is how we take the help of our Mother Earth.

01:43:03.834 --> 01:43:09.709
Now, those who do not want to have Self-realization should leave this hall.

01:43:23.083 --> 01:43:28.209
