01:43:32.959 --> 01:43:38.999
So. Now let's have it, something that is so important for us.

01:43:45.209 --> 01:43:56.792
The another thing is that — as I am here only for today, and I'll come back after one year — I would also like to tell you how to raise your Kundalini yourself.

01:44:07.042 --> 01:44:16.000
Because even if it is awakened and breaks through, but again goes back to the places where you require energy.

01:44:26.542 --> 01:44:35.709
So, after realization all of you should attend the workshop and understand what is happening within yourself.

01:44:43.876 --> 01:44:46.417
Where is the problem and how to correct it.

01:44:50.751 --> 01:44:57.000
Also you must know what… what is the decoding of this message on the fingertips.

01:45:04.709 --> 01:45:13.999
And also you should know how to give realizations to others and fix them up, fix their Kundalini up for ever.

01:45:23.626 --> 01:45:27.751
Also you will learn how to cure yourself and cure others.

01:45:33.042 --> 01:45:35.876
And for all this you don't have to pay any money.

01:45:40.292 --> 01:45:46.959
But in the beginning, I would request you not to bring all the relations who are sick.

01:45:55.584 --> 01:45:57.584
First you all become the doctors.

01:46:00.959 --> 01:46:07.792
And then start treating the people whom you want to treat or to help.

01:46:15.584 --> 01:46:18.417
So, first you have to be well equipped.

01:46:19.834 --> 01:46:21.292
You have to be well equipped.

01:46:25.167 --> 01:46:32.250
All right. Now, the second thing is to put your left hand towards Me this way, which is very simple.

01:46:38.584 --> 01:46:42.501
Now, this represents your desire to get Self-realization.

01:46:49.834 --> 01:46:54.375
And with the right hand we start releasing our chakras one by one.

01:47:00.042 --> 01:47:03.334
And I'll tell you how to do it in proper way.

01:47:07.459 --> 01:47:09.999
Because the right hand is for action.

01:47:13.167 --> 01:47:23.042
And you have to sit very comfortably, to put both feet on the ground, straight touching the ground, in the parallel way.

01:47:30.167 --> 01:47:38.250
Put the left hand like this, and the right hand is to be used for touching different centres on the left-hand side.

01:47:49.542 --> 01:47:52.918
Now, I'll tell you first you have to touch your heart.

01:47:57.125 --> 01:47:59.709
In the heart resides the spirit.

01:48:04.083 --> 01:48:10.626
Now, you have to put your right hand now in the upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:48:18.167 --> 01:48:18.751
Now.

01:48:19.751 --> 01:48:25.667
You have to take this hand there because this is the centre of your mastery.

01:48:31.918 --> 01:48:37.125
Now, you have to take your hand in the lower part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:48:41.999 --> 01:48:45.667
This is the centre of pure knowledge of the Divine.

01:48:51.667 --> 01:48:56.459
Now. Here, when you start moving up, the Kundalini moves up with you.

01:48:56.626 --> 01:49:04.667
So now you put your hand again back on the centre of your mastery in the upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:49:15.999 --> 01:49:18.709
Now, take this right hand on your heart.

01:49:22.250 --> 01:49:31.542
Now, put this right hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder, and turn your head to your right.

01:49:42.042 --> 01:49:48.876
Please take it from the front, like that. Not this way, not this way.

01:49:55.501 --> 01:49:57.167
All right, now turn to your right.

01:49:59.292 --> 01:50:10.792
Now. This is a very important centre because most of the people catch it when you feel… I would say, when you feel guilty.

01:50:18.083 --> 01:50:23.459
Then take your hand on your forehead across and press it on both the sides.

01:50:30.417 --> 01:50:32.584
Here is the centre of forgiveness.

01:50:36.751 --> 01:50:42.375
Now. Take back your right hand on the back side of your head and push it back.

01:50:50.083 --> 01:50:53.501
This is the centre where you have to ask for forgiveness.

01:50:57.375 --> 01:50:58.999
Now stretch your hand fully.

01:51:01.667 --> 01:51:11.167
And the centre of your palm, you put it on top of your head, in the centre where it was a soft bone in the fontanelle bone area.

01:51:19.042 --> 01:51:20.459
Now move your scalp.

01:51:21.667 --> 01:51:29.375
Press it hard, push out your fingers, move your scalp clockwise seven times. Scalp.

01:51:40.792 --> 01:51:43.334
That's all. Now you have to close your eyes.

01:51:47.292 --> 01:51:50.751
Before that, I'll tell you what mistakes sometimes we'll commit.

01:51:55.042 --> 01:51:59.459
First is, your hand, left hand should be like this (shows Her hand palm up) and not like that (shows Her hand palm forward).

01:52:06.501 --> 01:52:07.292
Left hand.

01:52:09.292 --> 01:52:18.167
Second is that the second hand that you'll use, this hand should be taken from the front for this centre (puts Her right hand on Her left Vishuddhi).

01:52:27.250 --> 01:52:31.584
And again, not this way, but this way.

01:52:34.459 --> 01:52:36.834
Is very simple thing that we have to do.

01:52:37.167 --> 01:52:38.542
Now you can close your eyes.

01:52:38.501 --> 01:52:44.999
If you want, you can take out your spectacles also because it might be your eyesight might improve.

01:52:54.042 --> 01:52:56.999
Now, please don't open your eyes till I tell you.

01:53:01.292 --> 01:53:11.709
Now. Put the left hand towards Me and… you don't have to fight with yourself, don't have to fight with your thoughts, just be relaxed.

01:53:20.417 --> 01:53:23.584
Actually, you should be very pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:53:23.834 --> 01:53:27.834
(To a seeker) No, not like that. Now see, again I… just open your eyes.

01:53:28.792 --> 01:53:31.709
Put the hand like this comfortably on the table.

01:53:36.959 --> 01:53:38.834
Stretch the hand, yes.

01:53:39.125 --> 01:53:42.209
Not this way (stretches Her arm palm forward), not that way (stretches Her arm palm up), just on the table.

01:53:49.292 --> 01:53:55.042
Now, don't bend to much, don't make it back, but just sit straight, comfortably.

01:54:02.209 --> 01:54:13.125
Now, I've told you that you are at the epitome of your evolution and you should not feel guilty; on the contrary, you should be very pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:54:25.000 --> 01:54:27.417
First thing, you have to forgive yourself.

01:54:31.042 --> 01:54:39.375
Now, let us have your left hand like this, comfortably put, and both the feet little apart from each other.

01:54:39.626 --> 01:54:44.626
And now you close your eyes and put your right hand on your heart.

01:54:57.999 --> 01:55:04.125
Now, as I told you, in the heart resides the spirit, so you ask Me a very fundamental question.

01:55:09.751 --> 01:55:11.999
Put the fingers straight on the table.

01:55:20.292 --> 01:55:26.000
Please ask Me a question; you may address Me as Mother or Shri Mataji.

01:55:33.209 --> 01:55:37.667
So please ask the question three times: "Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:55:37.667 --> 01:55:39.667
Just ask the question. Three times.

01:55:59.250 --> 01:56:02.167
This question is very important.

01:56:02.417 --> 01:56:08.918
But this also means that if you are the spirit you are your master.

01:56:09.167 --> 01:56:21.501
So ask the second question, by putting your right hand in the upper part of your abdomen, upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side: "Mother, am I my own master?"

01:56:21.501 --> 01:56:23.501
Ask this question three times again.

01:56:57.792 --> 01:56:59.584
Now, take down your right hand.

01:56:59.584 --> 01:57:01.584
Please don't open your eyes, keep them closed.

01:57:07.375 --> 01:57:09.167
Don't you open your eyes at all.

01:57:12.334 --> 01:57:17.209
Now, put down your hand in the lower part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:57:23.626 --> 01:57:34.709
Here is the pure knowledge of the divine laws.

01:57:38.709 --> 01:57:40.250
But I cannot force you.

01:57:41.626 --> 01:57:54.709
So, I have to ask you to ask Me, like: "Mother, may I have the pure knowledge? Mother, please give me the pure knowledge."

01:58:16.042 --> 01:58:20.459
Ask this question six times because this centre has got six petals.

01:58:35.667 --> 01:58:40.626
By asking for pure knowledge, the Kundalini starts moving upward.

01:58:48.459 --> 01:58:59.876
So, now you raise your hand, right hand, in the up— in the lower part… upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:59:10.083 --> 01:59:20.167
Here, to open the centre, with full confidence please say: "Mother, I am my own master."

01:59:20.167 --> 01:59:21.667
Please say this ten times.

01:59:56.083 --> 01:59:56.709
Now.

01:59:58.584 --> 02:00:02.334
Please raise your right hand on your heart.

02:00:08.542 --> 02:00:16.167
To open this centre, you have to say with full confidence: "Mother, I am the spirit."

02:00:16.167 --> 02:00:20.626
Say it twelve times because this is the most fundamental truth.

02:00:53.417 --> 02:01:09.918
Now, raise your right hand to your neck, the corner between the neck and your shoulder, and place your head on the right-hand side.

02:01:18.584 --> 02:01:21.959
This is the centre caught when you feel guilty.

02:01:26.999 --> 02:01:31.667
So please say with full confidence: "Mother, I am not guilty."

02:01:42.250 --> 02:01:43.918
Say it sixteen times.

02:01:53.292 --> 02:02:04.334
Now, we have to know that the Divine is the ocean of love, compassion and bliss.

02:02:05.375 --> 02:02:09.167
But above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness.

02:02:09.792 --> 02:02:16.584
And there is nothing that cannot be dissolved by this ocean of forgiveness.

02:02:35.042 --> 02:02:44.250
But now if you feel guilty still, you can say it for hundred and eight times to punish yourself if you still feel guilty.

02:03:03.209 --> 02:03:07.876
Now, take your hand to your forehead.

02:03:12.626 --> 02:03:15.292
Keep your eyes closed, don't open them in between.

02:03:18.584 --> 02:03:20.250
And press it on both the sides.

02:03:24.999 --> 02:03:30.000
Now, here you have to say: "Mother, I forgive everyone."

02:03:36.542 --> 02:03:41.459
Maybe you might think that it is difficult.

02:03:45.167 --> 02:03:49.125
But whether you forgive or don't forgive, it's a myth.

02:03:50.209 --> 02:03:53.501
But if you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

02:04:03.083 --> 02:04:06.209
Just say it once, but from your heart.

02:04:12.584 --> 02:04:22.167
Now, you can take your right hand and put it on the back side of your head and allow your head to rest on it.

02:04:31.584 --> 02:04:35.959
Now, do not feel guilty or do not count your mistakes.

02:04:36.125 --> 02:04:45.584
Without feeling all that, you have to, just for your own satisfaction, say: "O Divine, if I have done anything wrong, please forgive me."

02:05:03.375 --> 02:05:08.417
Please put your hand on the back side of your head, back side, not on top. The back side.

02:05:13.792 --> 02:05:16.542
And push it upward. Now say it from your heart.

02:05:22.918 --> 02:05:34.542
Now stretch your hand fully, push back your fingers, and put the centre of your palm on the fontanelle bone area, which was a soft bone in your childhood, and press it hard.

02:05:46.792 --> 02:05:55.000
Now, stretch back your fingers, and press it hard, and press your scalp, moving clockwise seven times.

02:05:55.250 --> 02:06:05.000
At this time, you have to say that "Mother, please give me my realization," because I cannot force on your liberty.

02:06:29.459 --> 02:06:33.209
(To yogini) Because I do not want to force it on them.

02:06:33.792 --> 02:06:35.000
They have to ask for it.

02:07:23.000 --> 02:07:25.083
Now take down your hand.

02:07:27.375 --> 02:07:28.292
Put the left—

02:07:29.751 --> 02:07:31.959
Please open your eyes.

02:07:36.209 --> 02:07:42.459
Put your right hand towards Me like this.

02:07:47.459 --> 02:07:49.000
Like this, so high.

02:07:50.584 --> 02:08:03.292
And now raise your left hand and see for yourself, bend your head and see for yourself if there's a cool breeze coming out of your head.

02:08:17.667 --> 02:08:20.375
Now, you put your left hand towards Me.

02:08:25.125 --> 02:08:30.999
And bend your head and see with your right hand if there's a cool breeze coming out.

02:08:57.167 --> 02:09:05.334
Now, you again put your right hand and see for yourself if there's a cool breeze coming out of your head.

02:09:05.876 --> 02:09:08.959
Out of your fontanelle bone area, a cool breeze.

02:09:08.918 --> 02:09:11.751
Some people get it far away, some very near.

02:09:23.292 --> 02:09:24.999
You have to little bit bend your head.

02:09:31.792 --> 02:09:35.250
Now, put both the hands towards the sky.

02:09:39.459 --> 02:09:42.792
And now push back your head and ask the question.

02:09:50.501 --> 02:09:54.501
Ask the question: "Is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

02:09:55.167 --> 02:09:58.042
Or, ask the question: "Is this the Chaitanya?"

02:09:58.792 --> 02:10:05.834
Or, ask the question: "Is this the All-pervading Power of Divine Love?"

02:10:06.125 --> 02:10:08.626
Ask this question three times.

02:10:24.375 --> 02:10:26.250
Ask this question three times.

02:10:30.584 --> 02:10:34.999
Now please, you can put down your hands.

02:10:45.167 --> 02:10:46.667
Please put down your hands.

02:10:47.709 --> 02:10:58.042
All those who have felt the cool breeze on top of their heads or in their hands, please raise both your hands.

02:11:07.042 --> 02:11:08.250
I would like to see.

02:11:11.876 --> 02:11:12.626
Aah!

02:11:14.209 --> 02:11:15.167
Look at that!

02:11:17.250 --> 02:11:19.417
Surprising! Thank you very much!

02:11:23.709 --> 02:11:30.667
Some may not get it, maybe; they might get it next time.

02:11:31.292 --> 02:11:39.334
They should all go to the workshop and work it out.

02:11:51.167 --> 02:11:54.626
Those who have got it are the lucky ones.

02:11:56.000 --> 02:12:01.334
And those who haven't got it should not be disappointed, it can be worked out very easily.

02:12:12.375 --> 02:12:16.375
Now, I would like to meet all of you, those who want to meet Me.

02:12:16.501 --> 02:12:21.334
You can come one by one from here, and I would like to meet you all.

02:12:56.626 --> 02:13:00.667
(To a seeker) How are you? All right? You felt the cool breeze?

02:13:00.999 --> 02:13:02.000
SEEKER: Yes, Shri Mataji.

